26
00:01:35,580 --> 00:01:39,140
=Episode 22=
=Hello, Dear Girlfriend=

27
00:01:46,220 --> 00:01:47,060
Yang, you're here.

28
00:01:48,020 --> 00:01:48,860
Mr. Zhou.

29
00:01:50,340 --> 00:01:52,580
Mr. Zhou heard I was sick,

30
00:01:52,580 --> 00:01:53,560
so he came to visit me.

31
00:01:59,580 --> 00:02:00,660
Mr. Zhou, you're a busy man.

32
00:02:00,660 --> 00:02:01,560
Thank you

33
00:02:02,220 --> 00:02:03,400
for visiting him.

34
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:05,120
It's not a big deal.

35
00:02:05,540 --> 00:02:07,220
Mr. Jiang and I are good friends now.

36
00:02:07,220 --> 00:02:08,960
Now he's ill. Of course I'd come.

37
00:02:09,260 --> 00:02:10,780
Besides, I called you many times,

38
00:02:10,780 --> 00:02:11,620
but you didn't answer.

39
00:02:11,820 --> 00:02:13,980
I assumed that you were busy
taking care of Mr. Jiang

40
00:02:13,980 --> 00:02:15,220
and didn't have time,

41
00:02:15,220 --> 00:02:16,880
so I decided to come.

42
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:18,460
What's so important

43
00:02:18,460 --> 00:02:20,160
that you have to come here to tell me?

44
00:02:21,500 --> 00:02:23,760
It's an emergency.

45
00:02:24,380 --> 00:02:26,840
However, Mr. Jiang
just finished his surgery.

46
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:28,280
We'd better let him rest well.

47
00:02:28,620 --> 00:02:29,560
Shall we find a place

48
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:30,540
to talk?

49
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:31,780
Sorry,

50
00:02:31,780 --> 00:02:33,040
I'm here to take care of the patient.

51
00:02:33,260 --> 00:02:34,760
It's time for dinner.

52
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:36,560
I need to get him some food.

53
00:02:38,860 --> 00:02:40,080
