64
00:03:04,300 --> 00:03:06,300
The nurse will send dinner over later.

65
00:03:06,300 --> 00:03:07,560
I'll let her do it.

66
00:03:09,340 --> 00:03:10,360
Don't worry about me.

67
00:03:11,380 --> 00:03:12,680
