68
00:03:19,580 --> 00:03:20,420
Mr. Zhou.

69
00:03:21,300 --> 00:03:22,620
Let's find a place nearby

70
00:03:22,620 --> 00:03:23,460
and have a quick talk.

71
00:03:24,460 --> 00:03:26,080
Okay, nearby.

72
00:03:29,020 --> 00:03:30,120
Call me if you need anything.

73
00:03:31,620 --> 00:03:33,160
Remember to eat the egg custard.

74
00:03:34,740 --> 00:03:35,580
Let's go.

75
00:03:35,660 --> 00:03:36,760
Mr. Jiang, rest well.

76
00:03:37,020 --> 00:03:37,880
