149
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:25,200
is Jiujiang Property.

150
00:07:26,060 --> 00:07:27,620
Linjiang's business circle

151
00:07:27,620 --> 00:07:28,600
has started.

152
00:07:28,860 --> 00:07:29,920
In that case,

153
00:07:30,220 --> 00:07:31,180
it will

154
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:32,660
