of surrounding areas.

155
00:07:32,740 --> 00:07:33,900
The barren land

156
00:07:33,900 --> 00:07:34,740
will turn into

157
00:07:35,020 --> 00:07:36,300
a brand new

158
00:07:36,300 --> 00:07:37,640
