163
00:07:46,860 --> 00:07:47,960
and the bank needs good results.

164
00:07:48,340 --> 00:07:49,180
Mo, you don't have to

165
00:07:49,180 --> 00:07:51,520
talk to me in private again and again.

166
00:07:53,740 --> 00:07:55,100
