via other channels.

172
00:08:03,060 --> 00:08:04,400
So, Ms. Tang,

173
00:08:05,150 --> 00:08:06,380
please help the private enterprise.

174
00:08:07,140 --> 00:08:09,200
The amount of loan we want to apply

175
00:08:09,500 --> 00:08:11,380
is 70 percent of Linjiang's valuation.

176
00:08:11,380 --> 00:08:13,320
It's around 2 to 2.5 billion yuan.

177
00:08:13,540 --> 00:08:15,040
Once we get the loan,

178
00:08:15,740 --> 00:08:17,280
we'll do anything we need to do

179
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:19,420
and guarantee your safety.

180
00:08:19,420 --> 00:08:21,280
If it meets the requirements,
you'll get the loan.

181
00:08:21,860 --> 00:08:23,720
If not, you have to make adjustments.

182
00:08:23,900 --> 00:08:24,740
