185
00:08:27,540 --> 00:08:28,680
Okay, Yang.

186
00:08:29,220 --> 00:08:30,060
Don't be angry.

187
00:08:30,380 --> 00:08:31,320
I'll stop talking.

188
00:08:32,300 --> 00:08:33,140
