00:39:51,580 --> 00:39:52,800
she came early in the morning.

866
00:39:53,220 --> 00:39:54,620
She went to the top floor

867
00:39:54,620 --> 00:39:56,150
after dropping her bag
and changing clothes.

868
00:40:00,620 --> 00:40:01,660
Did Vice President Gao

869
00:40:01,660 --> 00:40:02,920
ask about me today?

870
00:40:03,960 --> 00:40:04,860
No.

871
00:40:04,860 --> 00:40:05,920
I asked Secretary Lin.

872
