874
00:40:12,820 --> 00:40:14,120
Having a meeting?

875
00:40:16,940 --> 00:40:17,960
Jiang Shiyan.

876
00:40:18,460 --> 00:40:19,640
I've bought some groceries.

877
00:40:21,380 --> 00:40:22,220
Mom.

878
00:40:22,860 --> 00:40:24,380
What took you so long

879
00:40:24,380 --> 00:40:25,400
