884
00:40:33,060 --> 00:40:34,100
It's not even noon yet.

885
00:40:34,100 --> 00:40:34,940
What's the rush?

886
00:40:34,940 --> 00:40:35,760
Didn't you say

887
00:40:35,760 --> 00:40:36,740
Tang shouldn't have takeouts

888
00:40:36,740 --> 00:40:37,980
for lunch every day?

889
00:40:37,980 --> 00:40:39,200
You need to make lunch for her.

890
00:40:39,200 --> 00:40:41,150
I'm going to order a flash delivery
to send the lunch to her.

891
00:40:41,500 --> 00:40:42,800
Did I say that?

892
00:40:43,020 --> 00:40:44,080
Yes, you did.

893
00:40:45,500 --> 00:40:46,900
Hello, flash delivery?

894
00:40:46,900 --> 00:40:48,220
